title: Chelsea Handler: A Joke about Touring
description: Chelsea Handler jokes about touring in her Netflix special, "Uganda Be Kidding Me". Grab your tickets at NetflixIsAJokeFest.com to see Chelsea and your other favorite comedians in the Netflix is a Joke Fest happening April 28th-May 8th in Los Angeles.
